Client
   ↓
API Gateway
   ↓
Order Service (create order)
   ↓
Inventory Service (RESERVE stock)
   ↓
Payment Service
   ↓
External Payment Gateway
   ↓
Order Service (CONFIRM order)
   ↓
Inventory Service (CONFIRM stock)
   ↓
Payment History Service
   ↓
Notification Service
   ↓
Response

